pullRequest.body:
An endomorphism of ` ModuleCat.restrictScalarsPseudofunctor`, i.e. a "compatible" family of functors `ModuleCat R â¥¤ ModuleCat R` for all (commutative) rings `R` induces a functor `PresheafOfModules R â¥¤ PresheafOfModules R` for any presheaf of (commutative) rings `R`. In particular, it should be possible to apply this to the exterior power functors in order to define the exterior powers of a presheaf of modules.

---

- [ ] depends on: #18197
